>Are warpy washers the VW equivalent of ordinary lock washers?

Spring or wavy washers are different.

>Are there studs / bolts on the engine where the use of warpy washers 
>is mandated?

I really don't know but finding metric wavy washers isn't hard in my area.  The places that seem to use them are the lowish torque studs like intake manifold, oil filler tube, oil cooler etc.

